ユーザーの設定に基づいて、Animation.localBounds変数が表示されない場合はアニメーションを無効にする。
Animation::ref::localBounds can be set by user, when culling is set to BasedOnUserBounds.
This culling method works better than BasedOnRenderers, because animation can push itself into the camera frustum.
SA: ::ref::BasedOnClipBounds, Animation::ref::localBounds property.